292 MVT LocVT, CCValAssign::LocInfo LocInfo,
293 ISD::ArgFlagsTy ArgFlags, CCState &State) {
294

296 if (!CC_Intel_OCL_BI(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
297 return false;
298 }
299
300 if (static_cast<const X86Subtarget&>(State.getMachineFunction().getSubtarget()).is64Bit()) {
301 if (!CC_X86_64(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
302 return false;
303 }
304
305 if (!CC_X86_32(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
306 return false;
307
308 return true; // CC didn't match.
309}

312static bool CC_X86_32(unsigned ValNo, MVT ValVT,
313 MVT LocVT, CCValAssign::LocInfo LocInfo,
314 ISD::ArgFlagsTy ArgFlags, CCState &State) {
315
316 if (State.getCallingConv() == CallingConv::X86_INTR) {
317 if (CC_X86_Intr(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
318 return false;
319 }
320
321 if (static_cast<const X86Subtarget&>(State.getMachineFunction().getSubtarget()).isTargetMCU()) {
322 if (!CC_X86_32_MCU(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
323 return false;
324 }
325
326 if (State.getCallingConv() == CallingConv::X86_FastCall) {
327 if (!CC_X86_32_FastCall(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
328 return false;
329 }
330
331 if (State.getCallingConv() == CallingConv::X86_VectorCall) {
332 if (!CC_X86_Win32_VectorCall(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
333 return false;
334 }
335
336 if (State.getCallingConv() == CallingConv::X86_ThisCall) {
337 if (!CC_X86_32_ThisCall(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
338 return false;
339 }
340
341 if (State.getCallingConv() == CallingConv::CFGuard_Check) {
342 if (!CC_X86_Win32_CFGuard_Check(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
343 return false;
344 }
345
346 if (State.getCallingConv() == CallingConv::Fast) {
347 if (!CC_X86_32_FastCC(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
348 return false;
349 }
350
351 if (State.getCallingConv() == CallingConv::Tail) {
352 if (!CC_X86_32_FastCC(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
353 return false;
354 }
355
356 if (State.getCallingConv() == CallingConv::GHC) {
357 if (!CC_X86_32_GHC(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
358 return false;
359 }
360
361 if (State.getCallingConv() == CallingConv::HiPE) {
362 if (!CC_X86_32_HiPE(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
363 return false;
364 }
365
366 if (State.getCallingConv() == CallingConv::X86_RegCall) {
367 if (!CC_X86_32_RegCall(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
368 return false;
369 }
370
371 if (!CC_X86_32_C(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
372 return false;
373
374 return true; // CC didn't match.

378static bool CC_X86_32_C(unsigned ValNo, MVT ValVT,
379 MVT LocVT, CCValAssign::LocInfo LocInfo,
380 ISD::ArgFlagsTy ArgFlags, CCState &State) {
381
382 if (LocVT == MVT::i1 ||
383 LocVT == MVT::i8 ||
384 LocVT == MVT::i16 ||
385 LocVT == MVT::v1i1) {
386 LocVT = MVT::i32;
387 if (ArgFlags.isSExt())
388 LocInfo = CCValAssign::SExt;
389 else if (ArgFlags.isZExt())
390 LocInfo = CCValAssign::ZExt;
391 else
392 LocInfo = CCValAssign::AExt;
393 }
394
395 if (ArgFlags.isNest()) {
396 if (unsigned Reg = State.AllocateReg(X86::ECX)) {
397 State.addLoc(CCValAssign::getReg(ValNo, ValVT, Reg, LocVT, LocInfo));
398 return false;
399 }
400 }
401
402 if (!State.isVarArg()) {
403 if (ArgFlags.isInReg()) {
404 if (LocVT == MVT::i32) {
405 static const MCPhysReg RegList1[] = {
406 X86::EAX, X86::EDX, X86::ECX
407 };
408 if (unsigned Reg = State.AllocateReg(RegList1)) {
409 State.addLoc(CCValAssign::getReg(ValNo, ValVT, Reg, LocVT, LocInfo));
410 return false;
411 }
412 }
413 }
414 }
415
416 if (!CC_X86_32_Common(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
417 return false;
418
419 return true; // CC didn't match.
420}

423static bool CC_X86_32_Common(unsigned ValNo, MVT ValVT,
424 MVT LocVT, CCValAssign::LocInfo LocInfo,
425 ISD::ArgFlagsTy ArgFlags, CCState &State) {
426
427 if (ArgFlags.isByVal()) {
428 State.HandleByVal(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, 4, Align(4), ArgFlags);
429 return false;
430 }
431
432 if (ArgFlags.isPreallocated()) {
433 State.HandleByVal(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, 4, Align(4), ArgFlags);
434 return false;
435 }
436
437 if (!State.isVarArg()) {
438 if (ArgFlags.isInReg()) {
439 if (LocVT == MVT::f32 ||
440 LocVT == MVT::f64) {
441 if (static_cast<const X86Subtarget&>(State.getMachineFunction().getSubtarget()).hasSSE2()) {
442 static const MCPhysReg RegList1[] = {
443 X86::XMM0, X86::XMM1, X86::XMM2
444 };
445 if (unsigned Reg = State.AllocateReg(RegList1)) {
446 State.addLoc(CCValAssign::getReg(ValNo, ValVT, Reg, LocVT, LocInfo));
447 return false;
448 }
449 }
450 }
451 }
452 }
453
454 if (!State.isVarArg()) {
455 if (LocVT == MVT::x86mmx) {
456 static const MCPhysReg RegList2[] = {
457 X86::MM0, X86::MM1, X86::MM2
458 };
459 if (unsigned Reg = State.AllocateReg(RegList2)) {
460 State.addLoc(CCValAssign::getReg(ValNo, ValVT, Reg, LocVT, LocInfo));
461 return false;
462 }
463 }
464 }
465
466 if (LocVT == MVT::i32 ||
467 LocVT == MVT::f32) {
468 unsigned Offset3 = State.AllocateStack(4, Align(4));
469 State.addLoc(CCValAssign::getMem(ValNo, ValVT, Offset3, LocVT, LocInfo));
470 return false;
471 }
472
473 if (LocVT == MVT::f64) {
474 unsigned Offset4 = State.AllocateStack(8, Align(4));
475 State.addLoc(CCValAssign::getMem(ValNo, ValVT, Offset4, LocVT, LocInfo));
476 return false;
477 }
478
479 if (LocVT == MVT::f80) {
480 unsigned Offset5 = State.AllocateStack(
481 State.getMachineFunction().getDataLayout().getTypeAllocSize(EVT(LocVT).getTypeForEVT(State.getContext())), Align(4));
482 State.addLoc(CCValAssign::getMem(ValNo, ValVT, Offset5, LocVT, LocInfo));
483 return false;
484 }
485
486 if (LocVT == MVT::v2i1) {
487 LocVT = MVT::v2i64;
488 if (ArgFlags.isSExt())
489 LocInfo = CCValAssign::SExt;
490 else if (ArgFlags.isZExt())
491 LocInfo = CCValAssign::ZExt;
492 else
493 LocInfo = CCValAssign::AExt;
494 }
495
496 if (LocVT == MVT::v4i1) {
497 LocVT = MVT::v4i32;
498 if (ArgFlags.isSExt())
499 LocInfo = CCValAssign::SExt;
500 else if (ArgFlags.isZExt())
501 LocInfo = CCValAssign::ZExt;
502 else
503 LocInfo = CCValAssign::AExt;
504 }
505
506 if (LocVT == MVT::v8i1) {
507 LocVT = MVT::v8i16;
508 if (ArgFlags.isSExt())
509 LocInfo = CCValAssign::SExt;
510 else if (ArgFlags.isZExt())
511 LocInfo = CCValAssign::ZExt;
512 else
513 LocInfo = CCValAssign::AExt;
514 }
515
516 if (LocVT == MVT::v16i1) {
517 LocVT = MVT::v16i8;
518 if (ArgFlags.isSExt())
519 LocInfo = CCValAssign::SExt;
520 else if (ArgFlags.isZExt())
521 LocInfo = CCValAssign::ZExt;
522 else
523 LocInfo = CCValAssign::AExt;
524 }
525
526 if (LocVT == MVT::v32i1) {
527 LocVT = MVT::v32i8;
528 if (ArgFlags.isSExt())
529 LocInfo = CCValAssign::SExt;
530 else if (ArgFlags.isZExt())
531 LocInfo = CCValAssign::ZExt;
532 else
533 LocInfo = CCValAssign::AExt;
534 }
535
536 if (LocVT == MVT::v64i1) {
537 LocVT = MVT::v64i8;
538 if (ArgFlags.isSExt())
539 LocInfo = CCValAssign::SExt;
540 else if (ArgFlags.isZExt())
541 LocInfo = CCValAssign::ZExt;
542 else
543 LocInfo = CCValAssign::AExt;
544 }
545
546 if (LocVT == MVT::x86mmx) {
547 unsigned Offset6 = State.AllocateStack(8, Align(4));
548 State.addLoc(CCValAssign::getMem(ValNo, ValVT, Offset6, LocVT, LocInfo));
549 return false;
550 }
551
552 if (static_cast<const X86Subtarget&>(State.getMachineFunction().getSubtarget()).isTargetDarwin()) {
553 if (!CC_X86_32_Vector_Darwin(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
554 return false;
555 }
556
557 if (!CC_X86_32_Vector_Standard(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
558 return false;
559
560 return true; // CC didn't match.
561}

565 MVT LocVT, CCValAssign::LocInfo LocInfo,
566 ISD::ArgFlagsTy ArgFlags, CCState &State) {
567

569 State.HandleByVal(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, 4, Align(4), ArgFlags);

1294static bool CC_X86_64(unsigned ValNo, MVT ValVT,
1295 MVT LocVT, CCValAssign::LocInfo LocInfo,
1296 ISD::ArgFlagsTy ArgFlags, CCState &State) {
1297
1298 if (State.getCallingConv() == CallingConv::GHC) {
1299 if (!CC_X86_64_GHC(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
1300 return false;
1301 }
1302
1303 if (State.getCallingConv() == CallingConv::HiPE) {
1304 if (!CC_X86_64_HiPE(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
1305 return false;
1306 }
1307
1308 if (State.getCallingConv() == CallingConv::WebKit_JS) {
1309 if (!CC_X86_64_WebKit_JS(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
1310 return false;
1311 }
1312
1313 if (State.getCallingConv() == CallingConv::AnyReg) {
1314 if (!CC_X86_64_AnyReg(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
1315 return false;
1316 }
1317
1318 if (State.getCallingConv() == CallingConv::Win64) {
1319 if (!CC_X86_Win64_C(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
1320 return false;
1321 }
1322
1323 if (State.getCallingConv() == CallingConv::X86_64_SysV) {
1324 if (!CC_X86_64_C(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
1325 return false;
1326 }
1327
1328 if (State.getCallingConv() == CallingConv::X86_VectorCall) {
1329 if (!CC_X86_Win64_VectorCall(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
1330 return false;
1331 }
1332
1333 if (State.getCallingConv() == CallingConv::HHVM) {
1334 if (!CC_X86_64_HHVM(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
1335 return false;
1336 }
1337
1338 if (State.getCallingConv() == CallingConv::HHVM_C) {
1339 if (!CC_X86_64_HHVM_C(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
1340 return false;
1341 }
1342
1343 if (State.getCallingConv() == CallingConv::X86_RegCall) {
1344 if (static_cast<const X86Subtarget&>(State.getMachineFunction().getSubtarget()).isTargetWin64()) {
1345 if (!CC_X86_Win64_RegCall(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
1346 return false;
1347 }
1348 }
1349
1350 if (State.getCallingConv() == CallingConv::X86_RegCall) {
1351 if (!CC_X86_SysV64_RegCall(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
1352 return false;
1353 }
1354
1355 if (State.getCallingConv() == CallingConv::X86_INTR) {
1356 if (CC_X86_Intr(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
1357 return false;
1358 }
1359
1360 if (static_cast<const X86Subtarget&>(State.getMachineFunction().getSubtarget()).isTargetWin64()) {
1361 if (!CC_X86_Win64_C(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
1362 return false;
1363 }
1364
1365 if (!CC_X86_64_C(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
1366 return false;
1367
1368 return true; // CC didn't match.
1369}

2885 return false;

2890 return false;
2891 }

2893 if (!RetCC_X86_32_C(ValNo, ValVT, LocVT, LocInfo, ArgFlags, State))
2894 return false;
2895
2896 return true; // CC didn't match.
2897}
